 - took us on a visit to them. And - remember this, that when we were in that house with these people - where we sat on a chair we had to sit on that chair until we left. That's how - how we were brought up.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did your mother ever take you shopping?
