No. Oh well - we were - kind of - sort of a poshed up on a Sunday, compared to the - the ordinary weekday. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did you play games on Sunday?
