Oh - well - it's hard to tell that. It's hard to - it just depends on her duties. You know, she worked in the - police station. You couldnae just - walk out of the police station, any more than.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did you go to Sunday school or not?
