 I saw you last, I've lay at nights some nights and I - thought some of these questions that - you put to me you know. I said - it's strange that these questions should - come to me, and here I am in bed, and I can answer some of them, that I couldnae ans
wer to the lady that was taking - this statement. You see? You see how it works out?
