ling that I had. You know. She just did - she just learned us what she - she put - what she knew }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7998066\charrsid1209268 how}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268  - she - just what she knew, or what she picked up herself. Because her life - working was busy. She had not time for - sitting down to read or write or anything like that.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 How old were you when you first went to school?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
How old was I? Oh now you're - you're - you're - you're driving me to - I'm - giving myself away like talking about it. Oh - oh - I just forget. I just forget now when I went to sc
hool. But I stuck it. I stuck it just the same. Until I left at - until I was the age to leave school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Can you remember what time of the morning you used to go to school?
