Oh yes, well - well wait a now - you could say now - oh well - I just forget what - how long you - had to be on railway, some retire before others you know. But - I know - I just - I'm trying to think. You know, if I could think out these thi
ngs before you come I would be ready for you. You know, I would be ready for you, but I'm not. Went into a single cabin. And - I didn't like being confined in the - in the - train register boy. I - I didn't like that, and - I left it and went on to the - 
platform, you know, so to speak. Porter or - ticket examine - ticket collector or something like that. That was -
