\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Money on - oh well - well - this would be - I don't know what you - how you'd have used them in your days. But we used to go in for McCullums and - ice cream and - the only thing we -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 How did you get on with the other people that you worked with?
