Oh yes, oh aye, oh they - treated me all right. If you did your work I don't see why - or I didn't - didn't see then why they should - get up against you if you're - doing a job and meeting their requirements.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 What did you feel about them?
