 the railway or I wouldn't have been as long as I was, on it, I wouldn't - been all the years I was on and then retired from it. I retire and - when I did retire I - I felt I - I felt - I felt retired and I would have liked to have carried on. I - I would
 have liked to have carried on.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did being in full time employment alter your attitude to school at all?

