\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 No. Never - dreamt of it, no.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did you serve an apprentices
hip or a training period for any of the jobs you did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 No. No. Just kept up in the same -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did you belong to any trade union?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
No, bar the railway. Bar the railway. The railway - the railway had their union, our railway, and have it to this day.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did you take part in any of its activities?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
I beg your pardon? No, no. No, you - you mean did I - was I active in the unions or anything like that? No. No I left that to the - fellows with the brains. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did you feel that the bosses or
 the employers and the workers had the same interests, or different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Had - the bosses and the employees? Employees, aye, employees - had the same interest? Well that's a - a difficult question to answer that, because - there were some bosses that you
 could never satisfy - there are bosses that you couldn't satisfy. You got these little - tantrums, you know, and try to get - try to get you on the wrong foot, you know, so to speak.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did you feel among the railwaymen that there were divisions of interest?

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
That there were some who wanted one thing out of their job and others who wanted something different?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Oh well - you'll get that anywhere. You'll get that little bit of - jealousy or - you know you'll get that little bit of jealo
usy. How is - she getting on or - how is he getting on Joe? I could just done it as equally as well, you know, that - the feelings that - that you have.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Some people say that in those days that there was a great division between trained crafts en and other workers, did you feel that was true or not?
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Well - in my - in my way of business, in my job - I never had much time to think about what other people were doing. Good luck to them if they had a - a better job and a better time than I had. Well, 
good luck to them. I never was jealous of - of any - my pals are in different jobs you know, my - pals as years gone on their - their - my }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7998066\charrsid1209268 pals are}{\rtlch\fcs1 
\af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268  - some had - some had real good jobs you know. But I never envied them, I've gone on just the same and -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Would you say that full time work changed your general attitude to life in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Not - not at all, not at all. No, not at all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 You used to do some part time work in the theatre?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Could you tell me something about it, you used
 to really do it just for the pleasure of it didn't you?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Yes. Well - it - it meant a - you were off the street. You were off the street. And - you were off the street, you're away from company and - out of trouble you know, and - you were meeting peo
ple - you're meeting people - in the theatre that you would never otherwise have met. When I told you about - some of the artists there that I - that I ran into in my time you know, it was a pleasure to meet these people. And I - I'll have to - some - som
etimes the boys'll say to me, hey Jimmy, do you mind so and so - he appeared in the Empire on such and such -
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
In the theatre at the turn of the century, about 1900 when you started in the theatre.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 '98. '98 I was a programme boy. I was a programme boy in '98.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 How did you get that job?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Just - just - well - in a way, my mother - worked in the theatre and it was through her influence - that I got on to being a programme boy. And then from programme boy to attendant. And then from attendant - onto the stage myself.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 What did you have to do as a programme boy?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Programme boy, just sell the programmes. Just sell the programmes at that time - you got a penny a dozen - a penny for a dozen then.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 And you sold them inside the theatre?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Yes, inside the theatre yes. And we start at - you start at - you start at maybe in the stalls, and you work your way every other night, balcony - balcony up into the gallery. The gallery was my worst }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7998066\charrsid1209268 - place, because you didna sell}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268  out - any - very - very many programmes in the gallery.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 How many of you were there?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Ay? How many programme boys? About four of us. Four programme boys, aye.

\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Were you allowed to stay and see the shows then?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Oh yes. Oh yes, when - when you were done - 
when you had - served all the programmes, when you served the people with programmes and we saw that they were satisfied, you could stand and watch the show. That's how I learned it myself. Yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did your mother ever tell you about what she did?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
She didna need to tell me, I knew what she did. I could see - I was a dresser you know. She was a dresser, she was cleaner at first. She was a cleaner at first and then got onto the - dressing - dressing the - the troupers you know, the troupers like what
 I was myself. And many a time I was dresser. If I told you all the shows that I've been in - you'd be amazed.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 What did you used to do in these shows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
In the - in the shows? Well, we - now - well say with Alec Hurley, remember he was playing the 
lead, that was one time and - when I was a young man. The Friendly Lead, you - you just went on with a crowd and you were maybe - you'd come on and sing - we are all pals together, you know, you just come on the - on the crowd that's all.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Would you get paid for that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Oh well - oh well now wait - wait now, keep your breath. Keep your breath. A shilling a night. Shilling a night. A shilling a night.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 This was all before the war was it?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Oh aye, yes, yes, yes, before the war. Yes. Before the war.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 What sort of shows would be on in this theatre?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Well - well I could - I could name a - a bagload of shows - that I - that I was - on as a super myself, that I was on as a super - there's George Green Company \{BLANK\} George Green company and the \{BLANK\}
 The bricklayers. And - a shole lot - a lot - a lot of these - with Fred Kitchen, was on with Fred Kitchem, and Private Potts and - Persevering Potts.
\par 
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 All kinds of variety shows?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 All variety shows, yes.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 You liked that work?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Oh I did, I enjoyed it, I enjoyed it. I enjoyed it. You see, my mother - my mother when she - used to come back - in between houses, and lift the programmes lift the old programmes from the first house. You know, }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 
\lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid7998066\charrsid1209268 she\rquote d}{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268  lift the programmes. And many a 
time when - I was on - I was on the stage - my mother would be standing down - the floor, see, down in the stalls and she'd be - speaking to some of the other women you know, that's my son. That's my - son.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 Did your brother ever do that?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 It wasn't his line?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 No. No.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 I'd like to ask you about your life at home after you left school.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Oh my life at home was always - well - it was up and down, we - you know, there was little things cropped up that - really - wasn't of much consequence. My mother looked after us and - we wanted for nothing you know as regards food and that like.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
Did starting full time work change your relationship with your mother in any way?
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9263804 JM  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 No. No. She was proud to - to know that I was working. She
 was proud to know that I was working.
\par }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid9049349 I  : }{\rtlch\fcs1 \af0 \ltrch\fcs0 \lang2057\langfe1033\langnp2057\insrsid13703802\charrsid1209268 
And what about with your brother, did your relationship change with your brother?
